data.description: Looking to be tucked away in the woods and to be the last house on a dead end street? This house has 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths with some updates done within the last few years. New roof and gutters in 2021, New flooring throughout the house in 2020 and a new updated primary bathroom in 2023. Nice size kitchen dining area, and 2 bedrooms have full baths.
